{"tid":637862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱要落車嘔　的士客跳青馬橋亡","createTime":"2018-04-22T08:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T18:03:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":77,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9ad068c6a417208efd28e71c2e18524ab6208d","tid":637862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369075?_ga=2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369075%3F_ga%3D2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=840de081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369075%3F_ga%3D2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=1a577671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369075?_ga=2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱要落車嘔　的士客跳青馬橋亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180422/large/0421laicwimg_0228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F0421laicwimg_0228.jpg&h=229b3f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■的士乘客下車跨越欄杆跳海，事後警員到場調查。黎志偉攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「爺爺以後陪唔到你喇！」六旬男子向孫兒發短訊告別後，昨凌晨乘的士往大嶼山，途經青馬大橋時騙得司機停車讓他下車嘔吐，但卻攀越欄杆一躍跳落62米下的海中，司機大驚報警。救援船隻搜索45分鐘後將男事主救起，惟經送院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾向孫發訊︰陪唔到你喇<br />\n<br />\n跳橋自殺男子姓文（63歲），任職司機，家住火炭穗禾苑，據悉他有酗酒習慣，家人屢勸未改，雙方不時為此爭執。前晚他與家人晚飯時並無異樣，其後他獨自外出。<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨2時許，他乘搭的士前往大嶼山，的士沿青嶼幹線駛經青馬大橋時，他聲稱欲嘔吐，49歲姓薛司機於是靠橋邊停車。不料文下車後，突然跨越圍欄一躍而下，直墮海中。<br />\n<br />\n司機見狀大驚，慌忙報警。水警及消防輪到場搜索，約45分鐘後發現事主在海面載浮載沉，將他救起時已陷於昏迷，消防輪將他送往青龍頭碼頭，再轉送醫院搶救，惟終告不治。警方並未撿獲遺書，但據稱，文事發前曾向孫兒發出手機短訊，稱「爺爺以後陪唔到你喇」，家人擔心不已，但一直聯絡不到他，不久便收到他自殺死亡的消息，傷心不已。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎志偉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爬頭互撞起爭執　平治漢貨車男觀塘繞道MMA<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n圍毆餐廳東主　兩男長洲落網"},{"pid":"6d7a2b4a45dcf099a7a13fa7945e8f0f3bd327eb","tid":637862,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":185,"score":-183,"quote":{"pid":"5a9ad068c6a417208efd28e71c2e18524ab6208d","tid":637862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369075?_ga=2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369075%3F_ga%3D2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=840de081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369075%3F_ga%3D2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=1a577671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369075?_ga=2.108126978.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱要落車嘔　的士客跳青馬橋亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180422/large/0421laicwimg_0228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F0421laicwimg_0228.jpg&h=229b3f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■的士乘客下車跨越欄杆跳海，事後警員到場調查。黎志偉攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「爺爺以後陪唔到你喇！」六旬男子向孫兒發短訊告別後，昨凌晨乘的士往大嶼山，途經青馬大橋時騙得司機停車讓他下車嘔吐，但卻攀越欄杆一躍跳落62米下的海中，司機大驚報警。救援船隻搜索45分鐘後將男事主救起，惟經送院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾向孫發訊︰陪唔到你喇<br />\n<br />\n跳橋自殺男子姓文（63歲），任職司機，家住火炭穗禾苑，據悉他有酗酒習慣，家人屢勸未改，雙方不時為此爭執。前晚他與家人晚飯時並無異樣，其後他獨自外出。<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨2時許，他乘搭的士前往大嶼山，的士沿青嶼幹線駛經青馬大橋時，他聲稱欲嘔吐，49歲姓薛司機於是靠橋邊停車。不料文下車後，突然跨越圍欄一躍而下，直墮海中。<br />\n<br />\n司機見狀大驚，慌忙報警。水警及消防輪到場搜索，約45分鐘後發現事主在海面載浮載沉，將他救起時已陷於昏迷，消防輪將他送往青龍頭碼頭，再轉送醫院搶救，惟終告不治。警方並未撿獲遺書，但據稱，文事發前曾向孫兒發出手機短訊，稱「爺爺以後陪唔到你喇」，家人擔心不已，但一直聯絡不到他，不久便收到他自殺死亡的消息，傷心不已。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎志偉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爬頭互撞起爭執　平治漢貨車男觀塘繞道MMA<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n圍毆餐廳東主　兩男長洲落網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d65d5085b821a1087229f1e4708be1e4af10618","tid":637862,"uid":22913,"like":591,"dislike":35,"score":556,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"仆街搭的是唔比錢 不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c634337d7358c666528f6be392cbb34247ce10d2","tid":637862,"uid":170512,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:22:26.000Z","msg":"好電影FEEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6921a40fefb5ccee4d4a6741c7bca0c2818187","tid":637862,"uid":127988,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"變左自殺勝地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fed9f64c599d03dd0b4f5b7e86ba3dca425cac","tid":637862,"uid":28972,"like":182,"dislike":2,"score":180,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"其實句野幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b286f389d26e8d6d